<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Richway says raises 25.53 mln rand.</title>
<headline>Richway says raises 25.53 mln rand.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>South Africa's Richway Retail Properties Ltd said on Monday that it had raised 25.53 million rand by issuing 5.94 million new linked units to a selected institution at an issue price of 430 cents each.</p>
<p>&quot;The proceeds of this issue will be utilised to fund new property developments,&quot; the firm said.</p>
<p>Each linked unit consists of one ordinary share linked to one variable rate debenture of 399 cents.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
